472
00:35:17.598 --> 00:35:19.634
-MAN 1: Dear Mr. Zamora.
-MAN 2: Dear Mr. Zamora.

473
00:35:19.669 --> 00:35:22.499
-WOMAN 1: Dear Mr. Zamora.
-KID 1: Dear Mr. Zamora.

474
00:35:22.534 --> 00:35:24.191
