475
00:35:24.225 --> 00:35:27.194
WOMAN 2: Sure. I believe
you saw an
egg-shaped spacecraft

476
00:35:27.228 --> 00:35:29.713
that had passengers
from off this earth.

477
00:35:29.748 --> 00:35:31.336
[MAN READING]

478
00:35:31.370 --> 00:35:33.407
WOMAN 3: I could go on
for a week
telling you what I've seen.

479
00:35:33.441 --> 00:35:37.618
KID 1: A boy in our school science fair had three pictures

480
00:35:37.652 --> 00:35:41.760
that looked just like
the flying saucer
you described.

481
00:35:41.794 --> 00:35:44.728
[MAN READING]

482
00:35:44.763 --> 00:35:47.973
WOMAN: As I have pictures
of a couple of egg-shaped shape ships taken...

483
00:35:48.007 --> 00:35:50.355
-I read about you
seeing a flying saucer.
-WOMAN: I'm a retired teacher.

484
00:35:50.389 --> 00:35:52.495
Well. you have a friend
who believes you.

485
00:35:52.529 --> 00:35:55.498
This saucer phenomenon has changed my life and ideas.

486
00:35:55.532 --> 00:35:58.535
[KID 3 READING]

487
00:35:58.570 --> 00:36:02.021
WOMAN: August 17. 1960.
our Red Bluff officers

488
00:36:02.056 --> 00:36:04.231
and dozens of people
saw a saucer.

489
00:36:04.265 --> 00:36:10.306
KID 4: Can you tell me
how long it stayed on Earth.
and other things like that?

490
00:36:10.340 --> 00:36:12.549
MARY: Then people started
making fun of him

491
00:36:12.584 --> 00:36:16.001
that he had seen little men
from outer space

492
00:36:16.035 --> 00:36:21.248
or this and that.
A whole bunch of dirty stuff.

493
00:36:23.250 --> 00:36:27.046
MAN: Lot of people asked me.
"Is that the reason
you quit the police force?"

494
00:36:27.081 --> 00:36:28.841
No. the reason
I quit the police force

495
00:36:28.876 --> 00:36:32.190
was because I was going
and doing a lot
of publicity and stuff.

496
00:36:32.224 --> 00:36:34.640
I didn't wanna hurt the town.

497
00:36:37.367 --> 00:36:42.924
NARRATOR: The level of inquiry
went all the way to the office of the President.

498
00:36:42.959 --> 00:36:48.689
To this day.
the Socorro close encounter
remains unexplained.

499
00:36:50.277 --> 00:36:52.348
VALLEE:
Socorro was very similar

500
00:36:52.382 --> 00:36:57.698
to the French cases
that I had brought
to Hynek's attention.

501
00:36:57.732 --> 00:37:02.772
Checked by the police.checked by the French Air Force.

502
00:37:02.806 --> 00:37:06.224
where there were also occupants
who were seen.

503
00:37:06.258 --> 00:37:10.711
short beings.
in connection with the objects.

504
00:37:13.023 --> 00:37:15.233
I think that's what
convinced him

505
00:37:15.267 --> 00:37:19.582
that there were UFO landings
in the United States.

506
00:37:29.177 --> 00:37:33.458
Looked like a toy top
somewhat upside down.

507
00:37:33.492 --> 00:37:36.978
So this is the diagram
which we've come up with.

508
00:37:37.013 --> 00:37:39.567
It's more flat here
other than round.

509
00:37:39.602 --> 00:37:41.742
But it does have the hump
up in here.

510
00:37:41.776 --> 00:37:44.745
It seemed to move off the groundif it was down.

511
00:37:44.779 --> 00:37:48.162
And then we saw three lights
that went from yellow to red.

512
00:37:48.196 --> 00:37:50.613
When you got right up to it.
it lit up.

513
00:37:50.647 --> 00:37:53.201
I mean. it really did
become bright.
and we could see it.

514
00:37:53.236 --> 00:37:56.204
the outline of it. real good.

515
00:37:56.239 --> 00:37:59.449
NARRATOR: Blue Book's
Dr. Allen Hynek investigated

516
00:37:59.484 --> 00:38:01.348
one of the alleged
landing sites

517
00:38:01.382 --> 00:38:04.212
with the local sheriff.

518
00:38:04.247 --> 00:38:07.733
At an overflow press conference later that day.

519
00:38:07.768 --> 00:38:11.772
the world held its breath
for an historic revelation

520
00:38:11.806 --> 00:38:14.499
about the landings in Michigan.

521
00:38:14.533 --> 00:38:19.469
Hynek. by now
privately convinced
of the UFO reality.

522
00:38:19.504 --> 00:38:22.369
struggled to follow
the Air Force policy

523
00:38:22.403 --> 00:38:25.337
of tamping down
public excitement.

524
00:38:25.993 --> 00:38:27.788
[MAN SPEAKING]

525
00:38:31.757 --> 00:38:37.591
I'm saying that the two cases
that I investigated
most deeply were most likely.

526
00:38:37.625 --> 00:38:41.698
I said in a statement
that I couldn't prove it
in a court of law.

527
00:38:41.733 --> 00:38:43.493
[MAN SPEAKING]

528
00:38:44.943 --> 00:38:46.324
No. that's not quite right.

529
00:38:46.358 --> 00:38:49.603
I think that a person can be
pretty sure about something

530
00:38:49.637 --> 00:38:52.433
without being ableto convict somebody of a murder.

531
00:38:52.468 --> 00:38:58.266
-Can you? Please.
-Yes. I do. Honestly.
in this case.

532
00:38:58.301 --> 00:38:59.923
[MAN SPEAKING]

533
00:39:01.131 --> 00:39:03.686
NARRATOR:
Hynek's strained explanation.

534
00:39:03.720 --> 00:39:06.861
which he later called
his greatest regret.

535
00:39:06.896 --> 00:39:09.381
ignited a public furor.

536
00:39:09.416 --> 00:39:11.521
MAN: Mr. Ford.
what about flying saucers?

537
00:39:11.556 --> 00:39:14.248
You've had some in Michigan
in the past week.

538
00:39:14.282 --> 00:39:20.703
GERALD: Dave. we've had
several incidents that many felt were sufficient

539
00:39:20.737 --> 00:39:24.085
to justify some action
by our government.

540
00:39:24.120 --> 00:39:28.849
and not the kind of
flippant answer that was given by the Air Force

541
00:39:28.883 --> 00:39:33.336
where they passed it off
as "swamp gas."

542
00:39:33.371 --> 00:39:38.168
It seems to me that this mystery does require

543
00:39:38.203 --> 00:39:40.550
that the Congress
take a good look at it.

544
00:39:40.585 --> 00:39:44.347
Let them put their record
on the line.

545
00:39:44.382 --> 00:39:50.595
NARRATOR: On April 5th. 1966.
congressional hearings
were held with Dr. Hynek

546
00:39:50.629 --> 00:39:55.772
and Secretary of the Air Force Harold Brown
both giving testimony.

547
00:39:58.119 --> 00:40:03.849
MAN 1: Mr. Ford has come out.
He has a pretty good-size
stature in the Congress.

548
00:40:03.884 --> 00:40:06.645
And so. Mr. Secretary.

549
00:40:06.680 --> 00:40:12.755
see if you can shed some light on these
highly illuminated objects.

550
00:40:12.789 --> 00:40:14.895
MAN 2: Mr. Secretary.
there have been charges

551
00:40:14.929 --> 00:40:18.277
that the Air Force
is hiding something
in the UFO field.

552
00:40:18.312 --> 00:40:21.349
We have not been
hiding anything.

553
00:40:21.384 --> 00:40:24.560
The investigations
have been made public.

554
00:40:24.594 --> 00:40:27.563
The hearing this morningwas public for just that reason.

555
00:40:27.597 --> 00:40:29.772
There has never been
any evidence

556
00:40:29.806 --> 00:40:32.637
presented to
the United States Air Force.

557
00:40:32.671 --> 00:40:35.294
or discovered by
the United States Air Force.

558
00:40:35.329 --> 00:40:38.125
which would indicate
that the UFO phenomena

559
00:40:38.159 --> 00:40:42.819
represents any interplanetary
space vehicle of any kind.

560
00:40:45.270 --> 00:40:48.135
NARRATOR:
Amid growing pressure.
the Air Force commissioned

561
00:40:48.169 --> 00:40:50.206
an outside panel of scientists

562
00:40:50.240 --> 00:40:55.936
to analyze select cases
and settle the matter
once and for all.

563
00:40:55.970 --> 00:40:59.077
It was headed
by physicist Edward Condon.

564
00:40:59.111 --> 00:41:04.323
Dr. Condon. do you hope
to find people from
outer space here on Earth?

565
00:41:04.358 --> 00:41:08.155
Well. I don't know for sure.
but we'll try to
just study the reports

566
00:41:08.189 --> 00:41:11.883
and get as much
additional information
as we can to see.

567
00:41:11.917 --> 00:41:16.888
REPORTER: Would you like
to have us being visited
by these little or big things?

568
00:41:16.922 --> 00:41:20.408
Well. that'd be fine with me.
I hope they're friendly.

569
00:41:20.443 --> 00:41:22.169
How do you propose
to go about...

570
00:41:22.203 --> 00:41:25.690
NARRATOR: After the project
was launched. Condon remarked to an audience

571
00:41:25.724 --> 00:41:29.176
that he thought
the UFO subject was nonsense.

572
00:41:29.210 --> 00:41:35.803
But "I'm not supposed to reach that conclusion
for another year."

573
00:41:38.116 --> 00:41:40.118
After a two-year investigation.

574
00:41:40.152 --> 00:41:44.571
the panel submitted
a massive 1.400 page report

575
00:41:44.605 --> 00:41:48.816
showing that many cases
were radar
and weather anomalies.

576
00:41:48.851 --> 00:41:53.372
but confirming a number
as truly unexplainable.

577
00:41:53.407 --> 00:41:56.341
Among them were
the famous McMinnville photos

578
00:41:56.375 --> 00:41:59.517
taken on the Trent family farm.

579
00:41:59.551 --> 00:42:04.004
as well as film footage of UFOs in Great Falls. Montana.

580
00:42:05.730 --> 00:42:08.249
NICK: As I looked up.
I saw two silvery objects

581
00:42:08.284 --> 00:42:10.079
moving swiftly
out of the northwest.

582
00:42:10.113 --> 00:42:14.566
No sound. except I thought
I heard a whooshing sound
when I first saw them.

583
00:42:14.601 --> 00:42:17.051
The discs appeared
to be spinning like a top.

584
00:42:17.086 --> 00:42:18.777
and were about 50 feet across.

585
00:42:18.812 --> 00:42:20.607
which was much slower
than the jets

586
00:42:20.641 --> 00:42:23.679
which shot by shortly
after I filmed the discs.

587
00:42:23.713 --> 00:42:27.924
I could not see any exhaust. wings or any kind of fuselage.

588
00:42:27.959 --> 00:42:31.963
They appeared to be
of a bright. shiny metal.
like polished silver.

589
00:42:35.035 --> 00:42:40.454
There are cases
that are not explainable
in conventional terms.

590
00:42:40.488 --> 00:42:45.148
There is the assumption
of intelligence
or intelligent control.

591
00:42:45.183 --> 00:42:49.946
but not necessarily
the assumption
of direct communication.

592
00:42:49.981 --> 00:42:53.501
Why are they here?
What are they doing?

593
00:42:53.536 --> 00:42:56.608
What do they want from us?
What are their motivations?

594
00:42:57.989 --> 00:43:01.579
NARRATOR: But it was Dr. Condon
who wrote the final word.

595
00:43:02.200 --> 00:43:03.995
[READING]

596
00:43:14.212 --> 00:43:19.907
I was kind of woolly
on that one.
You'd have to conclude

597
00:43:19.942 --> 00:43:25.706
that what we were looking at
was beyond our current state
of the knowledge.

598
00:43:25.741 --> 00:43:29.296
But it began to hit me
that Dr. Condon
has apparently not read

599
00:43:29.330 --> 00:43:31.298
his own material very carefully.

600
00:43:31.332 --> 00:43:33.887
You do an actual tabulation.
which he doesn't seem
to have done.

601
00:43:33.921 --> 00:43:36.648
and you find his percentage ofunexplained is five to six times

602
00:43:36.683 --> 00:43:37.925
larger than the Air Force.

603
00:43:37.960 --> 00:43:40.031
And yet. what is his
principal recommendation?

604
00:43:40.065 --> 00:43:42.965
The principal recommendation
that Dr. Condon
has come through with

605
00:43:42.999 --> 00:43:46.002
is there's nothing
of scientific interest
that warrants further attention

606
00:43:46.037 --> 00:43:48.626
on the part
of the federal government
here in any major way.

607
00:43:48.660 --> 00:43:51.421
He recommends
dropping the whole problem.

608
00:43:51.456 --> 00:43:56.668
Nobody could get funded.
Nobody would look
at the data seriously

609
00:43:56.703 --> 00:44:00.672
because of the prestige
of the academy

610
00:44:00.707 --> 00:44:02.881
saying that the problem
had been solved.

611
00:44:02.916 --> 00:44:06.678
The Air Force closed
their reporting system.

612
00:44:06.713 --> 00:44:09.992
so that if the public
wanted to report something.

613
00:44:10.026 --> 00:44:12.373
they would report it
to the local police.

614
00:44:12.408 --> 00:44:14.755
But it would never get
to the attention

615
00:44:14.790 --> 00:44:18.897
of scientists really examining
the phenomena.

616
00:44:20.554 --> 00:44:26.905
NARRATOR: In 1969. the Air Force officially ended its public investigations.

617
00:44:29.459 --> 00:44:32.083
Which would suggest what?

618
00:44:32.117 --> 00:44:33.809
That they knew what it was?

619
00:44:35.431 --> 00:44:36.950
Or didn't know what it was.

620
00:44:38.054 --> 00:44:41.713
Also the other way.
And they did know what it was.

621
00:45:05.392 --> 00:45:08.809
NARRATOR: One aspect
of the phenomenon
that was swept under the rug

622
00:45:08.844 --> 00:45:12.744
was the pervasive reporting
of UFO intrusions

623
00:45:12.779 --> 00:45:17.093
at the world's most sensitive military facilities.

624
00:45:17.128 --> 00:45:20.752
Details did not come to light
until decades later

625
00:45:20.787 --> 00:45:24.618
at the National Press Club
in Washington. DC.

626
00:45:25.861 --> 00:45:30.520
Declassified US government
documents and witness testimony

627
00:45:30.555 --> 00:45:33.869
from former or retired
US military personnel

628
00:45:33.903 --> 00:45:40.116
confirmed. beyond any doubt.
the reality
of ongoing UFO incursions

629
00:45:40.151 --> 00:45:41.980
at nuclear weapon sites.

630
00:45:42.015 --> 00:45:45.501
What you have heard here today
is evidence of a phenomenon.

631
00:45:45.535 --> 00:45:48.607
It sounds fantastic.
and it is fantastic.

632
00:45:49.850 --> 00:45:53.198
In 1967.
I was a missile launch officer

633
00:45:53.233 --> 00:45:55.787
stationed at Malmstrom
Air Force Base. Montana.

634
00:45:55.822 --> 00:46:00.792
NARRATOR: Malmstrom was
America's first line
of nuclear defense.

635
00:46:00.827 --> 00:46:03.622
its silos packed
with Minutemen missiles.

636
00:46:03.657 --> 00:46:09.974
Each one nearly 100 times
more powerful than the bomb
that devastated Hiroshima.

637
00:46:11.182 --> 00:46:15.220
Launch officers could. within minutes of confirmation.

638
00:46:15.255 --> 00:46:22.227
send their birds arcing
6.000 miles to incinerate
key Soviet cities.

639
00:46:22.262 --> 00:46:25.783
triggering a war
that would end
our civilization.

640
00:46:39.866 --> 00:46:42.420
I was the chief of party.
I was the observer.

641
00:46:42.454 --> 00:46:47.183
Basically what I was doing
was the star observation
to provide precise

642
00:46:47.218 --> 00:46:51.636
latitude and longitude
on our small three-man team.

643
00:46:51.670 --> 00:46:55.398
Came from the north
and stopped right over us.

644
00:46:55.433 --> 00:47:01.094
and it had a white light
from the center.
looking down into this island.

645
00:47:01.128 --> 00:47:04.200
I just said to myself.
"What if this thing beams us up

646
00:47:04.235 --> 00:47:06.616
and takes us off
to some distant place

647
00:47:06.651 --> 00:47:08.308
and never returned
to Earth again?"

648
00:47:08.342 --> 00:47:11.863
I mean. this is going through
my head here
while this thing's above me.

649
00:47:11.898 --> 00:47:15.902
And then from this dead stop.
it shoots off to the east.

650
00:47:15.936 --> 00:47:18.836
It's just like now you see it.
now you don't. It just...

651
00:47:22.909 --> 00:47:25.808
MAN: The strike team
that went out.
they saw something.

652
00:47:37.613 --> 00:47:39.166
NARRATOR: Lt. Salas
was stationed

653
00:47:39.201 --> 00:47:41.893
in his underground
launch control capsule

654
00:47:41.928 --> 00:47:46.587
when he received a frantic call from one of his topside guards.

655
00:47:46.622 --> 00:47:47.865
MAN: Screaming into the phone.

656
00:47:47.899 --> 00:47:51.627
saying they're looking
at a red glowing object

657
00:47:51.661 --> 00:47:54.216
hovering just above
our front gate.

658
00:47:54.250 --> 00:47:59.911
Our missiles began going intowhat's called a no-go condition.or unlaunchable.

659
00:47:59.946 --> 00:48:01.326
Essentially. they were disabled.

660
00:48:03.846 --> 00:48:09.507
NARRATOR: In fact. ten missiles
began going offline
in a matter of seconds.

661
00:48:09.541 --> 00:48:11.474
one after the other.

662
00:48:14.719 --> 00:48:18.136
Personally. I'm never aware
of two missiles going down
at the same time.

663
00:48:18.171 --> 00:48:19.241
let alone ten.

664
00:48:19.275 --> 00:48:20.967
I was a top-secret
control officer

665
00:48:21.001 --> 00:48:24.177
and I passed down
nuclear launch authenticators.

666
00:48:24.211 --> 00:48:28.353
I can clearly recall a message
coming through my
communications center

667
00:48:28.388 --> 00:48:31.909
which basically said
that a UFO did. in fact.

668
00:48:31.943 --> 00:48:35.809
shut down several missile silos
in Montana.

669
00:48:41.435 --> 00:48:44.611
MAN: I was on duty at Echo.
which is our
squadron command post.

670
00:48:44.645 --> 00:48:48.477
We had strike teams respond
to alarms from the missiles.

671
00:48:48.511 --> 00:48:50.168
They were
three to five miles away.

672
00:48:50.203 --> 00:48:53.137
And they said.
"Sir. for lack
of a better description.

673
00:48:53.171 --> 00:48:55.415
there's a flying saucer
hovering over that missile.

674
00:48:55.449 --> 00:48:58.970
and there's a beam
of reddish light
going down to it."

675
00:49:00.006 --> 00:49:01.421
It had to be
a data collection thing.

676
00:49:01.455 --> 00:49:04.217
I'm sure they scanned
the warhead or something.

677
00:49:08.738 --> 00:49:12.950
In 1980. I was reassigned from
the Pentagon to RAF Bentwater

678
00:49:12.984 --> 00:49:14.330
as a deputy base commander.

679
00:49:14.365 --> 00:49:16.160
At that time. Bentwaters
was one of the largest

680
00:49:16.194 --> 00:49:18.610
tactical fighter ranges
in the world.

681
00:49:18.645 --> 00:49:23.546
NARRATOR: It was also
the largest American
nuclear bomb storage depot

682
00:49:23.581 --> 00:49:24.720
in Europe.

