696
00:50:13.872 --> 00:50:16.358
Yeah. it's a strange.
small red light.

697
00:50:16.392 --> 00:50:19.464
HALT: And all the barnyard animals have gotten quiet now.

698
00:50:19.499 --> 00:50:20.465
Deathly calm.

699
00:50:20.500 --> 00:50:22.398
This is weird.

700
00:50:24.400 --> 00:50:27.162
One object approached us
at very high speed.

701
00:50:27.196 --> 00:50:29.647
MAN: Here he comes
from the side.
