703
00:50:34.721 --> 00:50:36.585
This is unreal.

704
00:50:36.619 --> 00:50:37.758
We stood there in awe.

705
00:50:37.793 --> 00:50:39.933
Was this a warning?

706
00:50:39.967 --> 00:50:41.762
Was this an attempt
to communicate?

707
00:50:41.797 --> 00:50:45.352
Was this a weapon.
or just a probe?

