00:51:20.111 --> 00:51:22.527
a dot come on the scope.

721
00:51:22.562 --> 00:51:25.565
and it just went like.
one dot at the beginning.

722
00:51:25.599 --> 00:51:28.015
then another dot.
then another dot.
and it was gone.

