00:51:28.050 --> 00:51:32.537
A nd then it made an immediate
right-hand turn and came
right towards the base.

724
00:51:32.572 --> 00:51:34.194
Just absolutely phenomenal.

725
00:51:34.229 --> 00:51:37.404
It's not like any radar target
I've ever seen.

726
00:51:37.439 --> 00:51:40.959
traveling at an extremely
high rate of speed.

727
00:51:40.994 --> 00:51:43.997
It passed over
the control tower.

728
00:51:44.031 --> 00:51:47.863
and then it stopped.
It was an orangish color.

729
00:51:47.897 --> 00:51:50.072
Sort of popped into my mind
at the time

730
00:51:50.107 --> 00:51:53.006
that somebody's flying
a basketball out here.

731
00:51:53.040 --> 00:51:56.906
There were. like.
lights around the center of it.

732
00:51:56.941 --> 00:51:58.977
It was more like portholes.

733
00:51:59.012 --> 00:52:02.119
And then you were seeing
the light from the inside.

734
00:52:02.153 --> 00:52:06.364
But it hovered momentarily.
reversed its course.

735
00:52:06.399 --> 00:52:09.988
and went back out
at a high rate of speed.

736
00:52:12.336 --> 00:52:15.235
NARRATOR: Even more alarming
incidents took place

737
00:52:15.270 --> 00:52:17.686
