758
00:53:33.865 --> 00:53:36.385
decade after decade.

759
00:53:37.110 --> 00:53:38.560
To me. it's pretty clear.

760
00:53:38.594 --> 00:53:42.115
"We're shining a light on this.
we're pointing it out.

